                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">šum ʾagame Kasa (the son of ras Sǝbḥat) is mentioned as the donor in Additio 2. His baptismal name, Wäldä ʾArägawi (cp. Mss. AMQ-011, MKL-006), has been written in the supplication formulas in a secondary hand, over erasures.&#xD;
